# [Architecture]: Chezmoi Ignore Patterns (Target-Path Convention)
# [Rationale]: Patterns below MUST match the TARGET path (relative to $HOME),
# NOT the source path in the repository (e.g., use '.config/foo', NOT 'dot_config/foo').

README.md
DEVELOPER_OS.md
repomix-output.xml
.gitignore
.chezmoidata.yaml

# [Rationale]: Prevent script templates from being deployed as physical files to $HOME.
.chezmoiscripts

# [Rationale]: Prevent internal data lists from polluting the XDG config directory.
.config/linux

# [Rationale]: GitHub Actions workflows are for the repository CI, not for the target $HOME.
.github
